<title>USA: Energy Research names Jerry Leitman as CEO.</title>
<headline>Energy Research names Jerry Leitman as CEO.</headline>
<dateline>DANBURY, Conn 1997-08-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Energy Research Corp said Monday it had appointed Jerry Leitman as president and chief executive officer of the company.</p>
<p>Leitman will replace Bernard Baker, it said.</p>
<p>Leitman was previously president of Switzerland's ABB Asea Brown Boveri's global air pollution control businesses, it added.</p>
<p>Energy Research develops fuel cells and batteries in cooperation with government, electric utility and major international industrial organizations.</p>
